caller_intent: Ricardo Castillo requests a certificate from Generability for a company (Martin Roys Drago) and inquires about a collection notice from Alianza Insurance Services, expressing confusion about a payment due on December 4th.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledges receipt of a voicemail/email about the certificate request.
Agent confirms the certificate is in the system and will send a copy.
Agent addresses the collection notice inquiry, noting the payment due date and acknowledging the confusion.
summary: Ricardo Castillo requested a Generability certificate for Martin Roys Drago and inquired about a collection notice from Alianza. The caller expressed confusion about the collection notice despite having a payment scheduled.
